1950;;The Avengers;;American;;John H. Auer;;Adele Mara, John Carroll;;adventure;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Avengers_(1950_film);;In 17th-century colonial Argentina, while trying to find his father's murderer, the adventurer Francisco Suarez is confronted with Colonel Luis Corral, who tries to usurp the Governor's seat. The Colonel is supposed to marry Maria Moreno, with whom Suarez falls in love.